name: Jungle Man
summary:
A True Mixed-Reality Adventure!
Never before has a game like this been available in MR. Turn your home into a vine-swinging obstacle course in Jungle Man—a fast, funny, and totally chaotic action-puzzler. Made exclusively for mixed reality on Meta Quest 3/3s. No controllers needed.

Just you, your hands, and an unstoppable jungle hero!
